<!DOCTYPE html>
<html class="light" lang="en"><head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
<title>Debate Topics Ready - Vocabulary Bank</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;900&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com?plugins=forms,container-queries"></script>
<script id="tailwind-config">
        tailwind.config = {
            darkMode: "class",
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    colors: {
                        "primary": "#135bec",
                        "background-light": "#f6f6f8",
                        "background-dark": "#101622",
                    },
                    fontFamily: {
                        "display": ["Inter", "sans-serif"]
                    },
                    borderRadius: {"DEFAULT": "0.25rem", "lg": "0.5rem", "xl": "0.75rem", "full": "9999px"},
                },
            },
        }
    </script>
</head>
<body class="bg-background-light dark:bg-background-dark text-[#111318] dark:text-white font-display overflow-hidden h-screen flex">
<aside class="w-64 flex-shrink-0 bg-background-light dark:bg-background-dark border-r border-[#e5e7eb] dark:border-[#1f2937] flex flex-col h-full z-20">
<div class="p-4 flex flex-col gap-1 border-b border-transparent dark:border-[#1f2937]">
<div class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-200 dark:hover:bg-gray-800 p-2 rounded-lg transition-colors">
<div class="w-6 h-6 rounded bg-primary flex items-center justify-center text-white text-xs font-bold">V</div>
<h1 class="text-[#111318] dark:text-white text-sm font-semibold leading-normal truncate">Vocab Bank</h1>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-gray-400 text-[16px] ml-auto">unfold_more</span>
</div>
</div>
<nav class="flex-1 overflow-y-auto px-2 py-2 flex flex-col gap-1">
<div class="mb-4">
<p class="px-3 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider">Favorites</p>
<a class="flex items-center gap-3 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-200 dark:hover:bg-gray-800 text-[#616f89] dark:text-gray-300 transition-colors group" href="#">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[20px]">book_2</span>
<span class="text-sm font-medium">All Words</span>
</a>
<a class="flex items-center gap-3 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-[#e0e7ff] dark:bg-primary/20 text-primary dark:text-white group" href="#">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[20px]" data-weight="fill">schedule</span>
<span class="text-sm font-medium">Debate Setup</span>
<span class="ml-auto text-xs bg-primary text-white px-1.5 rounded animate-pulse">Active</span>
</a>
</div>
<div>
<p class="px-3 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider flex justify-between items-center group cursor-pointer">
                Collections
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[16px] opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">add</span>
</p>
<a class="flex items-center gap-3 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-200 dark:hover:bg-gray-800 text-[#616f89] dark:text-gray-300 transition-colors" href="#">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[20px]">description</span>
<span class="text-sm font-medium">Reading List</span>
</a>
<a class="flex items-center gap-3 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-200 dark:hover:bg-gray-800 text-[#616f89] dark:text-gray-300 transition-colors" href="#">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[20px]">business_center</span>
<span class="text-sm font-medium">Business English</span>
</a>
<a class="flex items-center gap-3 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-200 dark:hover:bg-gray-800 text-[#616f89] dark:text-gray-300 transition-colors" href="#">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[20px]">forum</span>
<span class="text-sm font-medium">Idioms</span>
</a>
<a class="flex items-center gap-3 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-200 dark:hover:bg-gray-800 text-[#616f89] dark:text-gray-300 transition-colors" href="#">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[20px]">inventory_2</span>
<span class="text-sm font-medium">Archive</span>
</a>
</div>
</nav>
<div class="p-3 border-t border-[#e5e7eb] dark:border-[#1f2937]">
<button class="flex w-full cursor-pointer items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-lg h-9 bg-primary text-white text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors shadow-sm">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]">add</span>
<span>New Word</span>
</button>
<div class="mt-3 flex items-center gap-2 px-2 text-[#616f89] dark:text-gray-400 cursor-pointer hover:text-primary transition-colors">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[20px]">settings</span>
<span class="text-sm font-medium">Settings</span>
</div>
</div>
</aside>
<main class="flex-1 flex flex-col h-full overflow-hidden bg-white dark:bg-[#0b0f17]">
<header class="h-14 flex-shrink-0 border-b border-[#e5e7eb] dark:border-[#1f2937] flex items-center justify-between px-4 bg-white dark:bg-[#0b0f17] z-10">
<div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm">
<a class="text-[#616f89] dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-primary dark:hover:text-white transition-colors flex items-center gap-1" href="#">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]">home</span>
</a>
<span class="text-[#616f89] dark:text-gray-500">/</span>
<a class="text-[#616f89] dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-primary dark:hover:text-white transition-colors" href="#">Vocab Bank</a>
<span class="text-[#616f89] dark:text-gray-500">/</span>
<span class="flex items-center gap-1 text-[#111318] dark:text-white font-medium">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px] text-primary">topic</span>
                Debate Setup
            </span>
</div>
<div class="flex items-center gap-3">
<div class="relative group">
<span class="absolute left-2.5 top-1.5 material-symbols-outlined text-gray-400 text-[20px]">search</span>
<input class="pl-9 pr-3 py-1.5 h-8 w-64 text-sm bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 border-none rounded-md focus:ring-1 focus:ring-primary text-[#111318] dark:text-white placeholder:text-gray-400 transition-all focus:w-80" placeholder="Search selected..." type="text"/>
</div>
<div class="h-4 w-[1px] bg-gray-300 dark:bg-gray-700 mx-1"></div>
<button class="p-1.5 text-gray-500 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-800 rounded-md transition-colors relative">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[20px]">notifications</span>
<span class="absolute top-1.5 right-1.5 w-2 h-2 bg-red-500 rounded-full border-2 border-white dark:border-[#0b0f17]"></span>
</button>
</div>
</header>
<div class="px-8 pt-8 pb-4 flex flex-col gap-6 flex-shrink-0">
<div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
<div class="flex items-center gap-3">
<div class="p-2 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-[32px]">topic</span>
</div>
<div>
<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#111318] dark:text-white tracking-tight">Topic Clustering</h1>
<p class="text-[#616f89] dark:text-gray-400 text-sm mt-1">Organize your 6 selected root words into debate topics. The AI will use these topics to structure the argument.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex justify-between items-center border-b border-[#e5e7eb] dark:border-[#1f2937] pb-4">
<div class="flex items-center gap-4">
<div class="flex bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 p-1 rounded-lg">
<button class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 text-[#111318] dark:text-white shadow-sm rounded-md text-sm font-medium transition-all flex items-center gap-2">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]" data-weight="fill">view_kanban</span>
                        Board
                    </button>
<button class="px-3 py-1.5 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-700 dark:hover:text-gray-200 rounded-md text-sm font-medium transition-all flex items-center gap-2">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]">list</span>
                        List
                    </button>
</div>
<div class="h-6 w-[1px] bg-gray-300 dark:bg-gray-700"></div>
<button class="flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-800 rounded transition-colors">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]">auto_fix_high</span>
                    AI Auto-Cluster
                </button>
</div>
<div>
<button class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-primary hover:bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-lg text-sm font-bold shadow-lg shadow-blue-500/20 transition-all transform hover:-translate-y-0.5">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[20px]">play_circle</span>
        Start Debate Session
    </button>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex-1 overflow-x-auto overflow-y-hidden px-8 pb-8">
<div class="flex gap-6 h-full pb-4 items-start min-w-max">
<div class="w-80 flex-shrink-0 flex flex-col h-full max-h-full">
<div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3 px-1 group cursor-pointer">
<h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-[#111318] dark:text-white flex items-center gap-2">
                        Personal Growth
                        <span class="px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 rounded text-xs">1</span>
</h3>
<div class="flex gap-1 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">
<button class="text-gray-400 hover:text-primary">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]">edit</span>
</button>
<button class="text-gray-400 hover:text-red-500">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]">delete</span>
</button>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex-1 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-[#161b26] rounded-xl p-3 overflow-y-auto flex flex-col gap-3 border border-transparent dark:border-gray-800">
<div class="bg-white dark:bg-[#1f2937] p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 cursor-grab active:cursor-grabbing group hover:border-primary/50 transition-all relative border-l-4 border-l-primary">
<span class="absolute top-2 right-2 text-gray-300 dark:text-gray-600 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]">drag_indicator</span>
<div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-1">
<div class="flex items-center gap-2">
<span class="font-bold text-[#111318] dark:text-white text-base">Grow</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[16px] text-gray-400" title="Root Word">park</span>
</div>
</div>
<p class="text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 line-clamp-1 italic mb-3">"Watch the nickels and dimes..."</p>
<div class="flex flex-col gap-2 pl-3 border-l-2 border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 my-3">
<div class="group/child flex items-center justify-between text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
<div class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[14px] text-gray-400">subdirectory_arrow_right</span>
<span class="font-medium">Grow up</span>
</div>
<span class="text-[10px] text-gray-400">Phrasal Verb</span>
</div>
<div class="group/child flex items-center justify-between text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
<div class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[14px] text-gray-400">subdirectory_arrow_right</span>
<span class="font-medium">Grow into</span>
</div>
<span class="text-[10px] text-yellow-600 dark:text-yellow-500">Learning</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex items-center justify-between pt-2 border-t border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700">
<span class="text-[10px] text-gray-400">Word Family • 3 items</span>
<button class="text-gray-400 hover:text-primary material-symbols-outlined text-[16px]">more_horiz</button>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="w-80 flex-shrink-0 flex flex-col h-full max-h-full">
<div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3 px-1 group cursor-pointer">
<h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-[#111318] dark:text-white flex items-center gap-2">
                        Business Strategy
                        <span class="px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 rounded text-xs">1</span>
</h3>
<div class="flex gap-1 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">
<button class="text-gray-400 hover:text-primary">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]">edit</span>
</button>
<button class="text-gray-400 hover:text-red-500">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]">delete</span>
</button>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex-1 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-[#161b26] rounded-xl p-3 overflow-y-auto flex flex-col gap-3 border border-transparent dark:border-gray-800">
<div class="bg-white dark:bg-[#1f2937] p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 cursor-grab active:cursor-grabbing group hover:border-primary/50 transition-all relative">
<span class="absolute top-2 right-2 text-gray-300 dark:text-gray-600 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]">drag_indicator</span>
<div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
<span class="font-bold text-[#111318] dark:text-white text-base">Bottom Line</span>
<span class="text-[10px] bg-teal-100 dark:bg-teal-900/30 text-teal-700 dark:text-teal-300 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded font-medium border border-teal-200 dark:border-teal-800">Idiom</span>
</div>
<p class="text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 line-clamp-2 mb-3">The final total of an account, or the crucial fact.</p>
<div class="flex items-center justify-between">
<span class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
<span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-yellow-500"></span>
<span class="text-[10px] font-medium text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Learning</span>
</span>
<button class="text-gray-400 hover:text-primary material-symbols-outlined text-[16px]">more_horiz</button>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="w-80 flex-shrink-0 flex flex-col h-full max-h-full opacity-60 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">
<div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3 px-1">
<h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider">New Topic</h3>
</div>
<button class="flex-1 min-h-[150px] bg-gray-50 dark:bg-white/[0.02] border-2 border-dashed border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-2 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-white/[0.05] hover:border-primary/50 text-gray-400 hover:text-primary transition-all group">
<span class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white dark:bg-[#161b26] shadow-sm flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[24px]">add</span>
</span>
<span class="text-sm font-medium">Create Topic Group</span>
</button>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</main>
</body></html>